Study Information Card

Source: R/out_StudyInformation.R
out_StudyInformation.Rd

Study Information Card

Usage

out_StudyInformation(dfGroups, dfResults)

Arguments

dfGroups

data.frame Group-level metadata dictionary.

dfResults

data.frame A stacked summary of analysis pipeline output. This will be filtered to cases where GroupLevel == "Site".

Value

A bslib::card() with overall study metadata.
